  "body": "- **I'm submitting a ...**\r\n  - [X] Bug report\r\n\r\n- **Bug Report**\r\nWhen signing a transaction with a Ledger Nano S, if I read through the prompts on the ledger to verify the transaction is what I expect, by the time I get through them all and confirm MEW has timed out the transaction.\r\n\r\nNote: When this happens, the UI gets into a state where I have to reset everything to proceed.  The confirmation dialog has to be closed, and when I close it the Read/Write contract (operation I was trying to do) is stuck with a spinner.  The only way to get past the spinner is to go back, which puts me back at a blank contract screen where I have to provide the ABI + address again.",
